---

<section id="problem" class="border-border scroll-mt-24 border-t bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">The problem</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">
          Most goals fail due to weak accountability and no real cost to missing
          them. Motivation fades, life gets busy, and intentions stay
          intentions.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-slate-700">
          <li>• No social pressure or support</li>
          <li>• No consequences for missing goals</li>
          <li>• Hard to keep consistent habits</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Placeholder class="aspect-video" label="Illustration placeholder" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
